=== VoxPopuli

VoxPopuli is a Ruby on Rails based quick poll creation app.

Create a question/poll, add some options to vote on and send out the link.

= Features

* Add any number of options to vote on
* Lock questions so no more options can be added
* See results of votes

= Upcoming features

* User authentication (only poll-creators can add options to vote on)
* IP/Cookie based system to enforce only one vote per question